Parma.John M. Annis House: The John M. Annis House is an American registered historic building, located in North Royalton, Ohio. It was listed in the U.S. National Register of Historic Places on March 19, 1992. John McClintock Annis was born February 26, 1804 at Phelps, Ontario, New York, USA, the son of Stephen and Christin Annis.
